<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Dinkelsbühl</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass Martin N., Kaplan in Nürnberg, seinem Recht beim nächsten Landgericht nach Egidiustag nachgeht, sofern er bis dahin nicht ausgerichtet wird.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_163" id="80v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_163_r1l11">Den von Dınkelſpühel </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_163_r1l12"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Merteins eins Capplans </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_163_r1l13">bey vns etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mıt <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_163_r1l14">Mertein vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> fleıſſıg <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt . Vnd <expan>könne<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_163_r1l15">dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> nıht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> an Jm <expan>erlange<ex>n</ex></expan> / Denn daʒ er der <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> dıe er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_163_r1l16">eẅch vnd den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> getan hat <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> aufſlag hat <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> bıs auf das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_163_r1l17">nehſt <expan>lantger<ex>icht</ex></expan> daʒ da wırdt nach ſand egıdıen tag ſchıerıſt / alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_163_r1l18">beſchehe Jm in der ʒeıt nıht ein <expan>auſʒrıchtu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vmb ſein ſprüche ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_163_r1l19">meynt er 
<add><ab facs="#facs_163_line_1577036523013_3831">denn </ab></add> <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> nachcʒufarn . da wıſſe ſıch eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> nach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_163_r1l20">ʒu <expan>rıchte<ex>n</ex></expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> / lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_163_r1l21"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Bartholomeȷ <expan>app<ex>oſto</ex>lȷ</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_163" id="80v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Dinkelspühel</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Merteins eins capplans bey uns etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Mertein umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> fleissig <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt;
                        und <expan>könne<ex>n</ex></expan> zu disen <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> an im <expan>erlange<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        denn daz er der <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>, die er ewch und den
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> getan hat,
                            <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> aufslag hat <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        bis auf das nehst <expan>lantger<ex>icht</ex></expan>, daz da wirdt <app>
<note><q type="date">nach sand Egidien tag
                                schierist</q>01.09.1420</note>
</app>. Also beschehe im in der zeit niht ein
                            <expan>auszrichtu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> umb sein sprüche, so meynt er
                            <add>denn</add>
<expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> nachczufarn; da wisse sich ewr
                                <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> nach zu
                            <expan>richte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Bartholomei
                        <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
